) AS 口座情報 ON ShokanKetteiTsuchiShoMeisaiTemp."kozaId" = 口座情報."uaT0310Koza_kozaId" WHERE (ShokanKetteiTsuchiShoMeisaiTemp."sashitomeHiHokenshaNo" IS NOT NULL AND ShokanKetteiTsuchiShoMeisaiTemp."sashitomeHiHokenshaNo" <> '' AND ShokanKetteiTsuchiShoMeisaiTemp."shikyuHushikyuKetteiKubun" = '1')
OR ShokanKetteiTsuchiShoMeisaiTemp."hihokennshaKubunCode" = #{資格区分}
) SELECT ShokanKetteiTsuchiShoMeisaiTemp.*,
FROM ShokanKetteiTsuchiShoMeisaiTemp LEFT OUTER JOIN
( SELECT ARRAY_AGG(CAST (ShokanKetteiTsuchiShoMeisaiTemp."shikibetsuCode" AS TEXT)) FROM ShokanKetteiTsuchiShoMeisaiTemp )
AS "ShikibetsuTaisho" ON ShokanKetteiTsuchiShoMeisaiTemp."shikibetsuCode" = "ShikibetsuTaisho"."shikibetsuCode" ORDER BY
${出力順},
ShokanKetteiTsuchiShoMeisaiTemp."hiHokenshaNo" ,ShokanKetteiTsuchiShoMeisaiTemp."serviceTeikyoYM" ,ShokanKetteiTsuchiShoMeisaiTemp."seiriNo"
